reviewText: i have watched lots of gay/lesbian shows and some are better than others,i haven't seen this one either,but it sure looks good,it really turns me on even though i'm very inexperienced by my own choices,but however i would love a round #2 one day with a mister rite..thanks amazon for giving us lots of choices in our viewing pleasures..shop @ home it's taken me a long tyme to admit that i'd rather eat @ the hotdog stand than muff dive totally gross 2 me girls you can have my slice of the pie 4-ever...boy/boy-girl/girl,yes..boy/girl...not 4-me...no thanks...
